  "instructions": [
    "Heat the iron teppan vessel over medium heat.",
    "Melt the unsalted butter and add smoked paprika, garlic powder, and black pepper. Stir well.",
    "Open the jar of glassy-jelly and pour it over the butter mixture, stirring until combined.",
    "Continue to heat and stir for about 5 minutes, until the jelly is warm and bubbly.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning with more smoked paprika, garlic powder, or black pepper if needed.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh cilantro if desired."
